    "industrial_process_notes": "Not industrially polymerized -- biosynthesized by plants (and some bacteria) and extracted from wood pulp (kraft/sulfite pulping) or cotton fiber (~90% cellulose by mass; wood ~40-50%). Regeneration processes (viscose, cuprammonium) convert extracted cellulose into rayon/cellophane -- see viscose-rayon and cellophane entries.",
